trans-unit.source: Provides location mapping support for script resources.
trans-unit.target: 提供指令碼資源的位置對應支援。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping> object can contain a collection of mappings to script resources, such as a script file (.js).
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping>物件可以包含的指令碼的資源，例如指令碼檔案 (.js) 的對應集合。

trans-unit.source: Each item in the collection maps to a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition> object by using either a name or name/assembly pair.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的每個項目對應至<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition>物件名稱 / 組件組。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition" /> object to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition" /> 物件新增至 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The name of the script resource.
trans-unit.target: 指令碼資源的名稱。
